{"tid":137661,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"勁量 Energizer 推出 Android 三防電話","createTime":"2017-02-28T03:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T12:08:05.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5dca90b25f02dab8bac516c02a88266f8be703e","tid":137661,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:53:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">勁量 Energizer 推出 Android 三防電話<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/02/28/energizer-rugged-android-phone/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2Fenergizer-rugged-android-phone%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=11e45216\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/02/28/energizer-rugged-android-phone/mobile-phone/</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/bbeten/1188901403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fbbeten%2F1188901403.jpg&h=016b8374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提起 Energizer，讀者們可能馬上聯想到電池產品，日前這個電池品牌竟然嘗試染指智慧電話界，發表了一款三防電話 Energy E550LTE。除了擁有陽剛的三防造型，最大賣點就是 4,000mAh 大容量電池和雙鏡頭設計，屬三防電話中較少見的設計。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqbOn62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqbOn62.jpg&h=deb0be22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEnergizer Energy E550LTE 擁有 5.5 吋 1080p 解像度屏幕，搭配 MediaTek MT6755 處理器、4GB RAM 和64GB 儲存。雙鏡頭設計分別為 13MP 和 8MP，前置鏡頭亦為 8MP，機背相機下方設有指紋辨識。11.1mm 厚的 Energy E550LTE 有 IP68 防塵防水級數，11,1mm 的機身厚度內置支援快速充電的 4,000mAh 電池。Energy E550LTE 將會在今年上市，定價為 449 美元（約 3,485 港元）。"},{"pid":"0b65fe49cc6b57e1793e3683aa9a2571e0a51500","tid":137661,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"點解唔用筆芯電"},{"pid":"a58180b1c790448f6f1c9f5b0f0b901f50065a56","tid":137661,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T04:04:37.000Z","msg":"買部行山玩澗用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1d835de404bd733e918f389e0eb3be1d3daaed","tid":137661,"uid":59552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"點解成日都用垃圾MTK"},{"pid":"95eeeba012d7e85c8e77ef0ab82e29225f87ae20","tid":137661,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:27:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解成日都用垃圾MTK</blockquote><br />\n好想嘔"},{"pid":"c459a47349d49fd4f028c8a1243a8ad36c0fd214","tid":137661,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解成日都用垃圾MTK</blockquote>在商言商"},{"pid":"a2c9f6f73e8c2d01640f3b50da98f8066cc98c5f","tid":137661,"uid":78379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:42:22.000Z","msg":"見到MTK可以出返去了。"},{"pid":"17f1a66736bae41beed0493e1cbcbd330e92e19a","tid":137661,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到MTK可以出返去了。</blockquote><br />\nMTK唔係好慳電㗎咩"},{"pid":"0dc1165e837e66238728ed1a6e48ea4f0a5cff28","tid":137661,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見到MTK可以出返去了。</blockquote><br />\nMTK唔係好慳電㗎咩</blockquote><br />\n唔打機話夠用既"},{"pid":"c136677b66220ac12b18c7546c62deb6552aa7d7","tid":137661,"uid":33694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:06:32.000Z","msg":"不如買cat 果部<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有埋ir camera<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c87fd3e39da4e0a10a777d3df30fbb2cdd4ee0","tid":137661,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:08:05.000Z","msg":"貼牌大陸機??"}]}